{"sessionKey":"42nd3rd40b","paragraphs":[{"html":"<a name=\"StartOfColumns\"></a><b><i>The House met at 1:30 p.m.</i></b>","index":"00000","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Madam\nSpeaker:</b> Good afternoon, everybody. Please be seated.","index":"00001","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Madam Speaker:</b> Introduction\nof bills? ","index":"00002","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Alan</b><b>�<a name=\"_Toc67472239\">Lagimodiere</a></b><b>�(Chairperson):</b>\nMadam Speaker, I wish to present the second report of the Standing Committee on\nJustice. ","index":"00003","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Clerk (Ms. Patricia Chaychuk):</b>\nYour Standing Committee on Justice presents� ","index":"00004","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Some Honourable Members:</b> Dispense.\n","index":"00005","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Madam Speaker:</b> Dispense. ","index":"00006","speaker":""},{"html":"<i>Your Standing Committee on\nJustice presents the following as its Second Report.</i>","index":"00007","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><i>Meetings</i></b>","index":"00008","speaker":""},{"html":"<i>Your Committee met on March 22,\n2021 at 6:00 p.m. in Room 255 of the Legislative Building.</i>","index":"00009","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><i>Matters under Consideration</i></b>","index":"00010","speaker":""},{"html":"<span lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"font-family:Symbol\">�<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><b><i><span lang=\"FR-CA\">Bill (No. 24)</span></i></b><i><span lang=\"FR-CA\"> � The Legal Profession Amendment Act / Loi modifiant la Loi sur la\nprofession d'avocat</span></i>","index":"00011","speaker":""},{"html":"<span lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"font-family:Symbol\">�<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><b><i><span lang=\"FR-CA\">Bill (No. 31)</span></i></b><i><span lang=\"FR-CA\"> � The Horse Racing Regulatory Modernization Act (Liquor, Gaming and\nCanna�bis Control Act a